 Functional Functions
вҖў The most common functions are getters
and setters
вҖ“ Getters retrieve the values of instance
variables and return them
вҖ“ Setters alter the values of the instance
variables

вҖў Why use these functions rather than
setting the variable to be public?
вҖў Control!

